{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"644affb695","title":"周恩来办公室给总政治部的通知","origin":"国家体委系统革命造反联络总部《体育前哨》第15期 1967年8月13日","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8677ebae01","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":4,"articleId":"644affb695"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1859b26ec5","type":"title","text":"周恩来办公室给总政治部的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"644affb695"},{"id":"54df296a76","type":"authors","text":"周恩来","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"644affb695"},{"id":"dbe95a0cbd","type":"paragraph","text":"八月四日上午11点30分，总政负责同志给国家体委系统革命造反联络总部来电，传达了关于体委由中央文革直接领导的指示。总政负责同志电话：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"644affb695"},{"id":"26a5b97541","type":"paragraph","text":"总理办公室于八月四日上午打电话通知总政：","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"644affb695"},{"id":"4438c36a80","type":"paragraph","text":"国家体委总政管不过来，决定由中央文革直接管，由戚本禹同志管。总政将从体委撤出来。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"644affb695"},{"id":"81cddd5368","type":"paragraph","text":"同日上午，中央文革也来电话通知：","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"644affb695"},{"id":"c4db0313f2","type":"paragraph","text":"中央文革派三名记者，到体委了解文化大革命情况。他们已于四日下午五时到达体委。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"644affb695"}],"page":{"id":"6d87f0ac3f","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"644affb695","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}